title: A Co and Fe bimetallic MOF with enhanced electrocatalytic oxygen evolution performance: exploring the electronic environment modifications upon Fe incorporation
content:
Energy Adv., 2024, 3,636-647
DOI: 10.1039/D3YA00572K, Paper
Open Access

Varsha Singh, Devesh Kumar Singh, Mamta Yadav, Smita Singh, Vikram Rathour, Ananya Tiwari, Vellaichamy Ganesan
The incorporation of iron into the cobalt-based metal–organic framework modifies the electronic environment and the resulting bimetallic MOF exhibits enhanced oxygen evolution reaction performance.
